sql_query.sql: SELECT "user_ips".* FROM "user_ips" WHERE "user_ips"."user_id" = $1 ORDER BY "user_ips"."user_id" ASC LIMIT $2

WITH first_degree AS ( SELECT target_account_id FROM follows WHERE account_id = 111360456210813785 UNION ALL SELECT 111360456210813785 ) SELECT accounts.*, (count(f.id) + 1) * ( (( greatest(0, coalesce(s.followers_count, 0)) / ( greatest(0, coalesce(s.following_count, 0)) + 1.0 ) ) + log( greatest(0, coalesce(s.followers_count, 0)) + 2 ) + ( case when s.last_status_at is null then 0 else exp( -1.0 * ( ( greatest(0, abs(extract(DAY FROM age(s.last_status_at))) - 30.0)^2) / (2.0 * ((-1.0 * 30^2) / (2.0 * ln(0.3))) ) ) ) end )) / 3.0 ) * ts_rank_cd(( setweight(to_tsvector('simple', accounts.display_name), 'A') || setweight(to_tsvector('simple', accounts.username), 'B') || setweight(to_tsvector('simple', coalesce(accounts.domain, '')), 'C') ), to_tsquery('simple', ''' username '':*'), 32) AS rank FROM accounts LEFT OUTER JOIN follows AS f ON (accounts.id = f.account_id AND f.target_account_id = 111360456210813785) LEFT JOIN account_stats AS s ON accounts.id = s.account_id WHERE accounts.id IN (SELECT * FROM first_degree) AND to_tsquery('simple', ''' username '':*') @@ ( setweight(to_tsvector('simple', accounts.display_name), 'A') || setweight(to_tsvector('simple', accounts.username), 'B') || setweight(to_tsvector('simple', coalesce(accounts.domain, '')), 'C') ) AND accounts.suspended_at IS NULL AND accounts.moved_to_account_id IS NULL GROUP BY accounts.id, s.id ORDER BY rank DESC LIMIT 10 OFFSET 0
